@startuml
title ChainFlow - System Sequence Diagram

actor "Data Engineer" as DE
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "FetcherClient" as Fetcher
participant "Infura RPC" as RPC
participant "Classifier" as Classifier
participant "External APIs" as ExtAPI
participant "GraphService" as Graph
participant "PostgreSQL" as PG
actor "Analyst" as Analyst
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "FastAPI" as Web

== Phase 1: Fetch ==

DE -> CLI : fetch --network ethereum --auto
CLI -> PG : get_latest_processed_block(ethereum)
PG --> CLI : block N
CLI -> RPC : eth_blockNumber
RPC --> CLI : latest block M
CLI -> Fetcher : fetch_logs(from=N, to=M, tokens)
loop adaptive chunks
    Fetcher -> RPC : eth_getLogs(fromBlock, toBlock, topics)
    RPC --> Fetcher : raw log array
    Fetcher -> Fetcher : decode_log() × n
    Fetcher -> PG : insert_transfers_batch(decoded_logs)
    Fetcher -> PG : insert_fetch_progress(chunk)
end

== Phase 2: Classify ==

DE -> CLI : classify_addresses --network ethereum
CLI -> ExtAPI : Dune Analytics (CEX wallets)
ExtAPI --> CLI : CEX address list
CLI -> PG : UPDATE transfers SET from_entity_class
CLI -> ExtAPI : 8004scan.io (x402 agents)
ExtAPI --> CLI : agent address list
CLI -> PG : UPDATE is_from_x402 = true

== Phase 3: Graph ==

DE -> CLI : graph --network ethereum
CLI -> Graph : run_pagerank_graph(ethereum)
Graph -> PG : SELECT from_address, to_address, SUM(value)
PG --> Graph : edge list
Graph -> Graph : build_graph(edges)
Graph -> Graph : compute_pagerank(G)
Graph -> PG : upsert_pagerank_scores(...)
Graph -> PG : upsert_pagerank_edges(...)

== Phase 4: Dashboard ==

DE -> Web : uvicorn src.web.main:app
Analyst -> Browser : http://localhost:8000/graph
Browser -> Web : GET /api/graph/scores?network=ethereum
Web -> PG : SELECT pagerank_scores + node labels
PG --> Web : scores + labels
Web --> Browser : JSON (nodes, edges, scores)
Browser -> Browser : render D3.js force graph

@enduml
